<br>
I don't think that the formula  &lt; Level X 32 + 1&gt;  is still an accurate guide.<br>
<br>
Here is a piece of emperical data , from last night.<br>
<br>
I am level 54 with base naked Hp of 1616 , self buffed and in normal combat gear my Hp is 2780.<br>
<br>
Last night while fighting Ixi , I had to LOH while at about 40% health. It restored 2280 HP (text message received), this is significantly more than my base HP. I was  raid buffed  to around 3500 hp at the time.<br>
<br>
The Formula would give  LoH = 54 x  (32 + 1) = 1782 Hp<br>
or  LoH = (54 x 32) +1  = 1629 hp<br>
This is low from my experience.<br>
<br>
I have no AAxp points spooled  yet. (And dont plan to spool any till level 60)<br>
<br>
Well, I hope this information helps the original poster, or anyone else trying to figure out the LoH.<br>
<br>
Sincerely Your brother in Arms,<br>
Rondal Trueknight , Level 54 Pally<br>
